 to give up my tap shoes,

160
00:09:09,172 --> 00:09:10,827
I shouldn't hit you in the
 head with them, should I?

161
00:09:10,827 --> 00:09:12,344
- I'm not following this, James.

162
00:09:12,344 --> 00:09:14,379
- You were wondering
 about his mother.

163
00:09:14,379 --> 00:09:16,137
- I gather we're
 changing the subject,

164
00:09:16,137 --> 00:09:17,137
and not very subtly.

165
00:09:17,137 --> 00:09:19,241
- May we, please?

166
00:09:19,241 --> 00:09:20,793
- I think his
 mother should know.

167
00:09:20,793 --> 00:09:23,827
Whether they're on speaking
 terms or not, he's her son.

168
00:09:23,827 --> 00:09:24,965
Where does she live?

169
00:09:24,965 --> 00:09:26,689
- Arkansas.

170
00:09:26,689 --> 00:09:28,517
Donald was born there.

171
00:09:31,862 --> 00:09:33,517
- Are you going to
 get in touch with her?

172
00:09:33,517 --> 00:09:34,724
- No.

173
00:09:34,724 --> 00:09:35,655
- Well, what about Donald?

174
00:09:35,655 --> 00:09:36,793
Doesn't he want her to know?

175
00:09:36,793 --> 00:09:38,034
- I'm not sure.

176
00:09:38,034 --> 00:09:39,724
- Well, ask him.

177
00:09:39,724 --> 00:09:40,551
- I did.

178
00:09:41,655 --> 00:09:43,517
We discussed it at length.

179
00:09:43,517 --> 00:09:44,931
We even went so far
 as to locate her.

180
00:09:44,931 --> 00:09:46,068
She's in the book,

181
00:09:46,068 --> 00:09:47,724
a place called, Fayetteville.

182
00:09:47,724 --> 00:09:48,551
- And?

183
00:09:50,000 --> 00:09:53,965
- He'd rather not tell her,
 than risk her not caring.

184
00:10:01,172 --> 00:10:03,344
- Why didn't I know all that?

185
00:10:03,344 --> 00:10:04,724
- All what?

186
00:10:04,724 --> 00:10:07,482
- About Donald and his mother,

187
00:10:07,482 --> 00:10:09,517
and where he's from and
 what happened between them,

188
00:10:09,517 --> 00:10:10,344
all that?

189
00:10:11,206 --> 00:10:13,827
- We know what we want to know.

190
00:10:16,275 --> 00:10:17,689
I'll be in touch.

191
00:10:30,448 --> 00:10:33,103
[phone dialing]

192
00:10:35,241 --> 00:10:37,137
- Oh, Audrey Grant, is he in?

193
00:10:37,137 --> 00:10:40,137
- They're promising
 a 14% return.

194
00:10:40,137 --> 00:10:41,689
If you believe that,
 they'll tell us another one

195
