196
00:10:44,586 --> 00:10:47,068
What we need.
 [buzzing]

197
00:10:47,068 --> 00:10:47,896
Hello?

198
00:10:49,896 --> 00:10:50,689
Oh.

199
00:10:53,137 --> 00:10:54,241
